_sText: I am proud to present you de_dust2_xt In current beta release! Dust2 is one of the Most massively played maps for counter-strike source, I decided to dedicate some time and extend the map in a new refreshed way. ( The final release will be in the CSS XT pack, for more information check out the studio) This version of dust2 is Mirrored !
